		INPUT AND OUTPUT
		----------------
Accepting input from the keyboard:-
---------------------------------
Stream:-
It represents flow of data from one 
place to another place.
There are 2 types of streams.
1.InputStream:- It reads (or) receive data
2.OutputStream:- It send (or) store(write) data to 
some other place.
=>All streams are represented as classes 
in java.io package (more than 50 classes).
